{"tid":2338296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Morey一年後接受espn採訪：支持他們並非無知的決定，而是有意識地表達聲援。","createTime":"2020-12-24T02:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T04:03:47.000Z","uid":161057,"like":70,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef5cf1b7583c23b4f7b4523b18d209877a192f2","tid":2338296,"uid":161057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"Philadelphia 76ers' Daryl Morey was worried Hong Kong tweet might end NBA<br />\ncareer<br />\n<br />\n莫雷曾非常憂心香港推特事件會終結自己的NBA生涯<br />\n<br />\n(以下節錄)<br />\n<br />\nWhat James did not know was that Morey had befriended a number of Hong Kong<br />\nresidents while attending business school and had intimate knowledge of the<br />\nchallenges they faced living in a semi-autonomous region. His decision to<br />\ntweet his support was neither rash nor uninformed, but a conscious effort to<br />\nexpress his solidarity for people he knew well.<br />\n<br />\nLBJ不知道的是，莫雷在商學院的時候結交不少香港人，<br />\n<br />\n也對半自治的香港所面對之議題有深度理解<br />\n<br />\n他的決定並非衝動或無知，而是有意識的支持自己熟知的人們<br />\n<br />\n&quot;In the last 12 months, I had moments where I thought I might never work in<br />\nthe NBA again, for reasons I was willing to go down for,&quot; Morey told ESPN<br />\nwhile discussing his new role with the 76ers. &quot;But I love working, I love<br />\nwhat I do, and I didn't want that to happen.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n過去一年來，我曾懷疑我將為了自己的堅持，而可能不能繼續待在NBA<br />\n<br />\n但是我愛工作，愛自己做的事情，不願意發生那樣的情況<br />\n<br />\nAsked months later if he regrets his decision to support the protests in Hong<br />\nKong, Morey paused for several seconds before responding, &quot;I'm very<br />\ncomfortable with what I did.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我對自己做過的事情非常坦然<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I was actually really, really worried about that,&quot; Morey said. He declined<br />\nto elaborate on the specific threats. &quot;Luckily I had [access to] different<br />\npeople who were assisting me with that and giving me advice on how to handle<br />\nit,&quot; he said. &quot;Hopefully, I've been able to get where we have some level of<br />\nsafety.<br />\n<br />\n我當時真的非常非常憂慮<br />\n<br />\n幸運的是我有不同的人在幫助我，給我處理問題的建議<br />\n<br />\n希望我已經到了比較安全的狀態<br />\n<br />\n&quot;But I was extremely concerned. You don't want the second-most powerful<br />\ngovernment on Earth mad at you, if you can avoid it. In this case, I<br />\ncouldn't.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我曾非常憂心<br />\n<br />\n若有選擇，你會不想要讓世界第二強大的政府對你出手，但我沒有選擇"},{"pid":"3cfc9eb7861b044f1dfd8c323ad0324bfb28fcd6","tid":2338296,"uid":161057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/NBA/M.1608773087.A.EF2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FNBA%2FM.1608773087.A.EF2.html&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76Md9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=2b2d5abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/NBA/M.1608773087.A.EF2.html</a><br />\n台仔連登cap過黎<br />\nMorey 好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebba8858294ad427d67c356f13d62a9b3c478ef7","tid":2338296,"uid":238920,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"賺既錢同名氣仲多過d奶共偽人既外國人都敢出聲<br />\n你班偽人為幾個臭錢走去做中共雞覺唔覺得醜"},{"pid":"a3f6f04ed733e57a7398071c220070058748fcf1","tid":2338296,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cfc9eb7861b044f1dfd8c323ad0324bfb28fcd6","tid":2338296,"uid":161057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/NBA/M.1608773087.A.EF2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FNBA%2FM.1608773087.A.EF2.html&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76Md9AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=2b2d5abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/NBA/M.1608773087.A.EF2.html</a><br />\n台仔連登cap過黎<br />\nMorey 好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T02:44:38.0